    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and is being sold as a reliable daily driver that needs some TLC. The exterior shows its age with some visible scratches, minor dings, and fading paint on the roof and hood. Inside, the upholstery has some staining and a small tear on the driver's seat, though all basic electronics remain functional. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, but it will likely need suspension work and a tune-up in the near future to ensure long-term reliability. It's a great project for someone looking for a solid base at a reasonable price point.",
      "price": 19500.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 17
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is recommended primarily for parts or as a comprehensive restoration project for an experienced mechanic. The engine currently exhibits severe performance issues, including significant smoke and loss of compression, and the transmission requires a full rebuild. The exterior has extensive rust damage and paint failure, while the interior shows heavy wear and several missing components. It is not currently roadworthy and will need to be towed from the lot.",
